e\", \"from\": 904, \"to\": 912}, {\"ngram\": \"two golds\", \"from\": 926, \"to\": 935}, {\"ngram\": \"a silver\", \"from\": 940, \"to\": 948}, {\"ngram\": \"another medal\", \"from\": 975, \"to\": 988}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's just a matter of what colour she gets.\\\"\", \"from\": 998, \"to\": 1042, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just a matter\", \"from\": 1003, \"to\": 1016}, {\"ngram\": \"what colour\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1031}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Monday night, Smith had to come from behind to win the 100m breaststroke final after China's Tang Qianting threw down the gauntlet with a blistering first 50m in the pool.\", \"from\": 1044, \"to\": 1218, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1132, \"end\": 1137, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999989223530414, \"rank\": 5.748427473102558e-07, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1140, \"end\": 1153, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tang_Qianting\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tang Qianting\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tang_Qianting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tang_Qianting\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Monday night\", \"from\": 1047, \"to\": 1059}, {\"ngram\": \"Smith\", \"from\": 1061, \"to\": 1066}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100m breaststroke\", \"from\": 1098, \"to\": 1119}, {\"ngram\": \"the gauntlet\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1177}, {\"ngram\": \"a blistering first 50m\", \"from\": 1183, \"to\": 1205}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 1209, \"to\": 1217}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Heyns says while she was confident that Smith would get a podium finish, even she was left surprised by the SA swimmer's push at the end of the 100m race to grab gold.\", \"from\": 1219, \"to\": 1386, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1327, \"end\": 1329, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.505683187795521e-16, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Heyns\", \"from\": 1219, \"to\": 1224}, {\"ngram\": \"Smith\", \"from\": 1259, \"to\": 1264}, {\"ngram\": \"a podium finish\", \"from\": 1275, \"to\": 1290}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1355}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100m race\", \"from\": 1359, \"to\": 1372}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1385}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was confident that Tatjana was going to get on the podium for the 100m breaststroke, but I did not know where she would finish as she was ranked fifth and there were two swimmers in that race that have gone faster than her, but I knew Tatjana is a fighter.\", \"from\": 1388, \"to\": 1647, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tatjana\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1417}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 1438, \"to\": 1448}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100m breaststroke\", \"from\": 1453, \"to\": 1474}, {\"ngram\": \"two swimmers\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1569}, {\"ngram\": \"that race\", \"from\": 1573, \"to\": 1582}, {\"ngram\": \"Tatjana\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1633}, {\"ngram\": \"a fighter\", \"from\": 1637, \"to\": 1646}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When I saw her in the heats and in the semi-finals, I thought that she would easily be in front of them for the whole way in the race, so Monday night was a little bit of a nail biter.\", \"from\": 1649, \"to\": 1834, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the heats\", \"from\": 1668, \"to\": 1677}, {\"ngram\": \"the semi\", \"from\": 1685, \"to\": 1693}, {\"ngram\": \"finals\", \"from\": 1694, \"to\": 1700}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 1740, \"to\": 1745}, {\"ngram\": \"the whole way\", \"from\": 1758, \"to\": 1771}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 1775, \"to\": 1783}, {\"ngram\": \"Monday night\", \"from\": 1788, \"to\": 1800}, {\"ngram\": \"a little bit\", \"from\": 1805, \"to\": 1817}, {\"ngram\": \"a nail biter\", \"from\": 1821, \"to\": 1833}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But, in terms of being confident of her grabbing gold, that confidence was more in the 200m breaststroke.\\\"\", \"from\": 1836, \"to\": 1942, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"terms\", \"from\": 1844, \"to\": 1849}, {\"ngram\": \"her grabbing gold\", \"from\": 1872, \"to\": 1889}, {\"ngram\": \"confidence\", \"from\": 1896, \"to\": 1906}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200m breaststroke\", \"from\": 1919, \"to\": 1940}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Smith will swim at the 200m breaststroke finals tonight (Thursday) together with her compatriot Kaylene Corbett, and the race will be shown live onShowmax, with the schedule suggestingit will get under way just after 21:00.\", \"from\": 1944, \"to\": 2167, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2040, \"end\": 2055, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaylene_Corbett\", \"score\": 0.9999999961760295, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kaylene Corbett\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaylene_Corbett\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaylene_Corbett\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Smith\", \"from\": 1944, \"to\": 1949}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200m breaststroke finals\", \"from\": 1963, \"to\": 1991}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 2061, \"to\": 2069}, {\"ngram\": \"the schedule suggestingit\", \"from\": 2105, \"to\": 2130}, {\"ngram\": \"way\", \"from\": 2146, \"to\": 2149}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She (Smith) is the highest decorated Olympian of all sports in South Africa,\\\" Heyns commented.\", \"from\": 2169, \"to\": 2264, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2207, \"end\": 2215, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999991984453602, \"rank\": 8.015552152563289e-07, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\":