s, and Tatjana does not compete in Short Course.\", \"from\": 2528, \"to\": 2674, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2568, \"end\": 2578, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.8085532369246131, \"rank\": 0.23444085827873268, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"World Cups\", \"from\": 2600, \"to\": 2610}, {\"ngram\": \"World Shorts\", \"from\": 2615, \"to\": 2627}, {\"ngram\": \"Tatjana\", \"from\": 2633, \"to\": 2640}, {\"ngram\": \"Short Course\", \"from\": 2661, \"to\": 2673}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The only thing that really matters for a lot of swimmers is the Olympic events.\", \"from\": 2675, \"to\": 2754, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The only thing\", \"from\": 2675, \"to\": 2689}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2714, \"to\": 2719}, {\"ngram\": \"swimmers\", \"from\": 2723, \"to\": 2731}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic events\", \"from\": 2735, \"to\": 2753}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"While Chad has one gold and three silvers, I think Tatjana trumps him.\", \"from\": 2756, \"to\": 2827, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2763, \"end\": 2767, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chad\", \"score\": 0.9999999416813824, \"rank\": 2.3242159967873475e-08, \"text\": \"Chad\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chad\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chad\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one gold\", \"from\": 2772, \"to\": 2780}, {\"ngram\": \"three silvers\", \"from\": 2785, \"to\": 2798}, {\"ngram\": \"Tatjana\", \"from\": 2808, \"to\": 2815}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I would like to see her break more world records.\", \"from\": 2828, \"to\": 2877, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more world records\", \"from\": 2858, \"to\": 2876}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Chad has two Short Course world records, and Tatjana has one Long Course world record that was only recently broken by a Russian swimmer.\\\"\", \"from\": 2878, \"to\": 3016, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2878, \"end\": 2882, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chad\", \"score\": 0.9999999416813824, \"rank\": 2.3242159967873475e-08, \"text\": \"Chad\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chad\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chad\"}, {\"begin\": 2999, \"end\": 3006, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"score\": 0.6142337719112018, \"rank\": 0.6269311112592697, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two Short Course world records\", \"from\": 2887, \"to\": 2917}, {\"ngram\": \"Tatjana\", \"from\": 2923, \"to\": 2930}, {\"ngram\": \"one Long Course world record\", \"from\": 2935, \"to\": 2963}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Heyns has also been impressed by South Africa's other swimmers in Paris and is excited to see Le Clos compete at the games.\", \"from\": 3018, \"to\": 3141, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3051, \"end\": 3063, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999999993669917, \"rank\": 6.330157629615607e-10, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}, {\"begin\": 3084, \"end\": 3089, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998376552, \"rank\": 1.6238689320962985e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Heyns\", \"from\": 3018, \"to\": 3023}, {\"ngram\": \"Le Clos\", \"from\": 3112, \"to\": 3119}, {\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 3131, \"to\": 3140}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Of course 